commit 4fd6e4196b8d56aa0ec97003f3675be3422fb393
Author: Michael Kleen <mkleen@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu May 9 12:41:20 2024 +0200

    Add memory accounting for multiphase execution
    
    Multi-Phase execution can produce large intermediate results which can
    cause out-of-memoryi errors. This adds memory accounting to prevent this.

